  <brief_title>Total Hip Arthroplasty Compared to Internal Fixation for Displaced Intracapsular Fractures of the Femoral Neck</brief_title>
  <official_title>Total Hip Arthroplasty Compared to Internal Fixation for Displaced Intracapsular Fractures of the Femoral Neck. A Randomized, Controlled Trial With a Seventeen Year Follow-up</official_title>
  <sponsors>
